a andral le Gibbaroskeri sas 95 potomki.
The ola manuša, savengere phure dada bešenas andre kala fori, visaľile pale: andral o Betlehem 123,
andral e Netofa 56,
andral o Azmavet 42,
andral o Kirjat-Jearim, andral e Kefira the andral o Beerot 743,
andral e Rama the Geba 621,
